title: My Neighbor Stole My Parking Spot
description:
This week on Unfazed and Unbothered, Tasia and Camo cringe at their snapchat memories, reminisce on their Golden Corral days, and Camo goes off about their mean neighbor who has absolutely no chill! Tune in to hear all the drama from Parkingate to front porch dog sh*t.
Go to GreenChef.com/unfazed130 and use code unfazed130 to get $130 off, plus free shipping!
Get your first birth control care package and donate to help more women in need of affordable birth control by going to THEPILLCLUB.COM/UNFAZED.
Listen to the Baby Mamas No Drama podcast wherever you get your podcasts.
Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube
